title: The Rise of Atlantis - Match 3 (Requested) [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Use your puzzle skills to raise the legendary continent of Atlantis 

from the depths of the Mediterranean Sea in this extraordinary 

challenge. Arrange game pieces into matching groups of three or more to 

collect the seven powers of Poseidon and restore fabled Atlantis. 

Puzzle your way through the ancient lands of Greece, Troy, Phoenicia, 

Babylon, Egypt, Carthage, and Rome in level after level of 

brain-bending fun. Featuring a stirring storyline, spectacular 

power-ups, and a bonus screensaver, The Rise of Atlantis is an original 

adventure for puzzle players everywhere.
